sections.title: The Campaign won't stop!
sections.description: We're making everything we can to make sure beach city and the planet earth is a better place to every living being. Came to see what we've done so far!

sections.title: Ask Amethyst
sections.description: Amesthyst is here to answer some of the questions you guys are asking! Let's hear her

questions.title: What if the diamonds decide to come after the gems here on earth?
questions.answer: The diamons are our friends now! Thanks to steven they are not a threat to earth or the gems around here. We can just chill and if they come around you can be sure its just for a visit.

questions.title: What about the cluster on the planet's core??
questions.answer: We have a protector now! Steven made sure that the cluster is no longer a threat, actually they helped us protect eath so many times now.

questions.title: The rent on New HomeWorld is getting to expensive! What's Steven going to do about it?
questions.answer: We promise you we'll develop a solution for the rent. Steven is at this moment trying to reach Bismuth so we can develop a great solution for everyone.
